"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-othersport-1932001-Olympics-2024-Noah-Lyles-USA-men-s-100m\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Noah Lyles produced an incredible late surge to pip Jamaica's Kishane Thompson to gold in the men's 100m race at the 2024 Olympics.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 133, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2, \"end\": 12, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noah Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\"}, {\"begin\": 54, \"end\": 61, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 0.9999999999595275, \"rank\": 3.826088315120431e-11, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}, {\"begin\": 72, \"end\": 80, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Klay_Thompson\", \"score\": 0.9161999291259397, \"rank\": 0.09146482995573248, \"text\": \"Thompson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Klay_Thompson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Klay_Thompson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 27-year-old set a new personal best to reign supreme over a rapid eight-man field, setting Paris' Stade de France alight with an electric showing.\", \"from\": 134, \"to\": 284, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 229, \"end\": 234, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999777174, \"rank\": 2.2320284474718827e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The runners kept their composure after an unwanted three-minute delay before being called to their blocks at the start line, but it was Lyles who stole the show.\", \"from\": 286, \"to\": 447, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 422, \"end\": 427, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"score\": 0.987704893816091, \"rank\": 0.012439108197447219, \"text\": \"Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Thompson looked destined to establish himself as the world's fastest man on his maiden Olympics appearance after starting strongly.\", \"from\": 449, \"to\": 580, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 449, \"end\": 457, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Klay_Thompson\", \"score\": 0.9161999291259397, \"rank\": 0.09146482995573248, \"text\": \"Thompson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Klay_Thompson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Klay_Thompson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Pick up your ultimate guide to the Olympics!\", \"from\": 582, \"to\": 626, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Going for Gold provides the day-by-day rundown of what's on and when.\", \"from\": 627, \"to\": 696, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Clickhereto buy.\", \"from\": 697, \"to\": 713, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He produced a 9.77 at the Jamaican Olympic trials and a 9.80 in the semi-finals - the quickest in Paris ahead of the final.\", \"from\": 715, \"to\": 838, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 741, \"end\": 749, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\", \"score\": 0.9548187954925099, \"rank\": 0.04731914025510276, \"text\": \"Jamaican\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\"}, {\"begin\": 813, \"end\": 818, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999777174, \"rank\": 2.2320284474718827e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Lyles - the reigning world champion - came out on top after an outstanding photo finish, clinching gold by five-thousandths of a second.\", \"from\": 840, \"to\": 980, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Lyles and Thompson had to wait to watch the reply back on the big screen to find out who had come out on top, it was that close.\", \"from\": 981, \"to\": 1109, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 991, \"end\": 999, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Klay_Thompson\", \"score\": 0.9161999291259397, \"rank\": 0.09146482995573248, \"text\": \"Thompson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Klay_Thompson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Klay_Thompson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Last year, the American superstar became the first man since Usain Bolt in 2015 to be named world champion in the 100m and 200m.\", \"from\": 1111, \"to\": 1239, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1126, \"end\": 1134, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9998629501063327, \"rank\": 0.00010809283235108554, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1172, \"end\": 1182, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Usain_Bolt\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Usain Bolt\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Usain_Bolt\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Usain_Bolt\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Many did not back him to win gold after he went slow in the heats and finished second behind Oblique Seville in the semi-finals.\", \"from\": 1241, \"to\": 1369, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1342, \"end\": 1349, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seville\", \"score\": 0.9999999998144631, \"rank\": 1.5324132420143654e