"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This also comes with anAmazon Prime 30-day free trial.\", \"from\": 1742, \"to\": 1796, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After silver-winner Thompson, the USA's Fred Kerley followed up his silver at Tokyo 2020 by picking up bronze with a seasonal best of 9.81.\", \"from\": 1798, \"to\": 1937, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1818, \"end\": 1826, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Klay_Thompson\", \"score\": 0.9161999291259397, \"rank\": 0.09146482995573248, \"text\": \"Thompson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Klay_Thompson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Klay_Thompson\"}, {\"begin\": 1832, \"end\": 1835, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9932943874277225, \"rank\": 0.0036730801544628596, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1838, \"end\": 1849, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Kerley\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Fred Kerley\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Kerley\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fred_Kerley\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"South Africa's Akani Simbine, Italy's reigning champion Marcell Jacobs, Botswana's Letsile Tebogo, the USA's Kenneth Bednarek and Jamaica's Seville completed the running order.\", \"from\": 1939, \"to\": 2115, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1939, \"end\": 1951, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 0.9999999361884895, \"rank\": 3.96680848414121e-08, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}, {\"begin\": 1954, \"end\": 1967, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Akani_Simbine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Akani Simbine\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Akani_Simbine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Akani_Simbine\"}, {\"begin\": 1969, \"end\": 1974, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9994369031591922, \"rank\": 0.0005239811203575519, \"text\": \"Italy\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1995, \"end\": 2009, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marcell_Jacobs\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Marcell Jacobs\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marcell_Jacobs\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marcell_Jacobs\"}, {\"begin\": 2011, \"end\": 2019, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\", \"score\": 0.999915400237469, \"rank\": 8.46060935915505e-05, \"text\": \"Botswana\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\"}, {\"begin\": 2042, \"end\": 2045, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9932943874277225, \"rank\": 0.0036730801544628596, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 2048, \"end\": 2064, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenny_Bednarek\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kenneth Bednarek\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenny_Bednarek\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenny_Bednarek\"}, {\"begin\": 2069, \"end\": 2076, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 0.9999999999595275, \"rank\": 3.826088315120431e-11, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}, {\"begin\": 2079, \"end\": 2086, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seville\", \"score\": 0.9999999998144631, \"rank\": 1.5324132420143654e-10, \"text\": \"Seville\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seville\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seville\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lyle's triumph makes him the first American to win Olympic gold in the men's 100m in 20 years since Justin Gatlin's success at Athens 2004.\", \"from\": 2117, \"to\": 2256, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Between Gatlin in Athens and Jacobs in Tokyo, Bolt dominated the event by winning three on the bounce in Beijing, London and Rio.\", \"from\": 2258, \"to\": 2387, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2276, \"end\": 2282, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2004_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.999999996313818, \"rank\": 3.6859595694933605e-09, \"text\": \"Athens\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2004_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2004_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2297, \"end\": 2302, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.8662270950965869, \"rank\": 0.15442643575663056, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}, {\"begin\": 2363, \"end\": 2370, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999949978, \"rank\": 5.080758092804289e-12, \"text\": \"Beijing\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2372, \"end\": 2378, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999999955798557, \"rank\": 2.2241520731510655e-09, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}, {\"begin\": 2383, \"end\": 2386, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999998485877882, \"rank\": 1.51412409658851e-07, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On BBC1 commentary, a breathless Steve Cram was in disbelief, saying: \\\"They are watching, they are looking.\", \"from\": 2389, \"to\": 2496, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2392, \"end\": 2396, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_One\", \"score\": 0.999941055270657, \"rank\": 5.894820419082633e-05, \"text\": \"BBC1\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_One\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_One\"}, {\"begin\": 2422, \"end\": 2432, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steve_Cram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Steve Cram\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steve_Cram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steve_Cram\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have never seen a finish this close.\", \"from\": 2497, \"to\": 2535, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That's it.\", \"from\": 2537, \"to\": 2548, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Lyles has his gold.\", \"from\": 2549, \"to\": 2568, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Unbelievable.\", \"from\": 2569, \"to\": 2582, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Thompson can only look on.\", \"from\": 2583, \"to\": 2609, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2583, \"end\": 2591, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Klay_Thompson\", \"score\": 0.9161999291259397, \"rank\": 0.09146482995573248, \"text\": \"Thompson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Klay_Thompson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Klay_Thompson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lyles did not even have a medal 10m out.\", \"from\": 2610, \"to\": 2650, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 2652, \"to\": 2761, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This may include adverts from us and 3rd parties based on our understanding.\", \"from\": 2762, \"to\": 2838, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 2839, \"to\": 2871, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy  \\\"He did not have a hope of winning.\", \"from\": 2872, \"to\": 2931, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He came fast, he came hard, and in the end, by the smallest of margins, he has taken the Olympic title.\", \"from\": 2932, \"to\": 3035, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Beaten in the heats, beaten in the semi-final, but he's won the one that mattered most.\\\"\", \"from\": 3037, \"to\": 3126, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"SEARCH  CONNECT WITH US  TODAY'S PAPER  See today's front and back pages, download the newspaper, order back issues and use the historic Daily Express newspaper archive.\", \"from\": 3128, \"to\": 3297, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3265, \"end\": 3278, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1765123173354322e-19, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"EXPRESS.CO.UK  Daily Express uses notifications to keep you updated\", \"from\": 32